1
00:00:00,310 --> 00:00:01,710
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,380
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:08,680
(Episode 35)

5
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:11,950
Ms. Kim.

6
00:00:18,360 --> 00:00:19,520
An anonymous tip claims...

7
00:00:22,590 --> 00:00:23,830
you held a press conference...

8
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:26,130
using a fraudulent appraisal report.

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:28,230
Do you admit to the allegation?

10
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:34,870
Are you sure the tip was anonymous?

11
00:00:50,090 --> 00:00:51,390
This appraisal report states...

12
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,530
that the jewel on the ornament
is genuine.

13
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:56,900
I memorized the serial number...

14
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,730
while Chairman Park was showing
the appraisal report...

15
00:00:58,730 --> 00:01:00,100
to an overseas agency.

16
00:01:00,770 --> 00:01:03,030
If you know the serial number,
you can request...

17
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,670
the appraisal report again
from the agency.

18
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:07,070
I see.

19
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:10,840
So should I turn this over
to the police?

20
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:16,280
Yes, a press conference was held
in Adele's name over this.

21
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,280
If you submit
this proof of authenticity...

22
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,120
with information
about a suspected deal...

23
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,720
between a company and a politician,

24
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:24,760
the case will be serious enough
that the police won't be able...

25
00:01:25,690 --> 00:01:27,130
to ignore it.

26
00:01:28,190 --> 00:01:29,190
However,

27
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:32,800
you must file the report
anonymously.

28
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:38,940
It's for your own safety
and to make my plan work.

29
00:01:40,710 --> 00:01:42,370
To ensure your plan works?

30
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:48,280
You'd be destroying
the reputation you've built...

31
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,910
as a gemologist over 20 years,

32
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:54,020
and, in a way, yourself.

33
00:01:54,390 --> 00:01:57,720
Do you really have to go this far
to stop the deal between...

34
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,920
Chairman Park and Assemblyman Kwon?

35
00:02:00,990 --> 00:02:04,260
There's only one thing
I can tell you right now.

36
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:10,200
The more power Chairman Park gets,
the more dangerous he becomes.

37
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,370
More dangerous?

38
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,770
I made that false appraisal...

39
00:02:15,410 --> 00:02:17,480
to stop Chairman Park Tae Ho.

40
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:21,150
But I can't let my actions
give him even more power.

41
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:25,280
Even if it means destroying myself,

42
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,250
I have to stop him.

43
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,390
Please help me.

44
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:36,690
I know how determined you are,

45
00:02:36,790 --> 00:02:39,360
so I can't talk you out of it
or deny your request.

46
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,230
As you wish,

47
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:45,170
I will report this to the police
along with the appraisal.

48
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:47,810
"President Kim Myung Hui
of Adele..."

49
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:50,710
"held a press conference
based on a false appraisal."

50
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:55,880
"She's trying to destroy evidence
at the Adele Gallery,"

51
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:58,220
"so you must arrest her
immediately."

52
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:03,190
Can't you tell me who the source is?

53
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,690
I already told you
the tip was anonymous.

54
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:10,330
Do you admit to the charge?
Just answer that.

55
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,860
I admit it.

56
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:15,600
I appraised an authentic piece...

57
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:18,470
as a fake.

58
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,570
Why?

59
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:25,740
Was it
on Chairman Park of Adele's orders,

60
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:29,350
or was it Assemblyman Kwon,
who owns the ornament?

61
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:36,090
I can't reveal everything just yet.

62
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:39,490
For my plan to work,
this is as far as I should go.

63
00:03:41,790 --> 00:03:43,600
It was an honest mistake.

64
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,660
Ms. Kim!

65
00:03:44,830 --> 00:03:49,030
I had to finish the appraisal
before the exhibition began,

66
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:52,400
and I made a mistake
because I was rushing.

67
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:56,540
It's all my fault
for not being good enough.

68
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:01,210
You're telling me
a top international gemologist...

69
00:04:01,550 --> 00:04:03,720
made a mistake like that
just because you were short on time?

70
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:07,920
Stop damaging your reputation
and come clean.

71
00:04:09,290 --> 00:04:12,120
I have nothing more to say.

72
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,330
I'm sorry.

73
00:04:19,230 --> 00:04:21,830
Wasn't using my marriage
for your own gain enough?

74
00:04:21,970 --> 00:04:25,140
Did you have to exploit
Mother's name and pride too?

75
00:04:25,570 --> 00:04:30,340
Tell them you ordered her to do it
and fix this mess now.

76
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,680
If you don't save her,

77
00:04:35,710 --> 00:04:37,450
I'll step in myself.

78
00:04:41,650 --> 00:04:43,960
As if you have the power
to fix this.

79
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:47,130
Do you have any idea
how important and serious this is?

80
00:04:48,030 --> 00:04:49,860
If you want this resolved,

81
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:53,100
stay out of it
and don't make things worse!

82
00:04:58,770 --> 00:05:00,910
We've just received word
from the legal team.

83
00:05:01,410 --> 00:05:02,770
What happened?

84
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:05,880
An anonymous tip came in
with the real appraisal certificate.

85
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,150
Given that it's a major case...

86
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:08,780
involving a corporation
and a politician,

87
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,280
they made a warrantless arrest...

88
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:12,950
to prevent evidence
from being destroyed.

89
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:15,920
Someone tipped off the police
with the real appraisal certificate?

90
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:17,390
What about my mother?

91
00:05:17,890 --> 00:05:19,020
Is she all right?

92
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:22,130
President Kim is insisting
it was just an honest mistake.

93
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:27,070
Since it was a warrantless arrest,
she'll be released within 48 hours.

94
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:29,630
My mother isn't someone
who makes mistakes.

95
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:34,710
Even now,
she's still protecting you.

96
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:38,540
How much more are you going
to put my mother through?

97
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:43,720
As a father, and as a husband,

98
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:47,320
you should be ashamed of yourself.

99
00:06:04,370 --> 00:06:06,500
- Assemblyman Kwon.
- Chairman Park.

100
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,910
What is all this mess?

101
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:12,810
You said it was all taken care of,
but now the whole thing's blown up!

102
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,850
I'll handle...

103
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:16,610
How will you handle this?

104
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,950
Reporters keep calling, accusing me
of falsifying the appraisal...

105
00:06:19,050 --> 00:06:20,790
to prevent
cultural asset designation.

106
00:06:21,290 --> 00:06:23,120
I'm at the point
where I have to donate the piece...

107
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,760
as a designated cultural asset.

108
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:29,460
You can forget about
the exclusive development rights.

109
00:06:29,530 --> 00:06:31,430
There's a long line of people
waiting to take your place!

110
00:06:39,770 --> 00:06:42,310
Use our contacts in the police
and get me answers.

111
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:45,710
Find out who the informant was.

112
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,250
I absolutely need to know.

113
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,550
I want the whole legal team on this.

114
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:58,690
Forget waiting the full 48 hours.
Get moving now.

115
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:04,060
Is the legal team heading out?
Then I'll go with them.

116
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:07,060
Secretary Jung,
you should come with me instead.

117
00:07:07,370 --> 00:07:08,770
Yes, of course.

118
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:12,540
- I'll pack a bag for Ms. Kim.
- All right.

119
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,200
(Division 1 Director's Office)

120
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:49,670
Did you look into
the police investigation?

121
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,910
It looks like there was
an anonymous tip.

122
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,050
An anonymous tip?

123
00:07:55,550 --> 00:07:56,550
Yes.

124
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:59,450
Given how things are going,

125
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:02,020
the exclusive development rights deal
Choi Yu Na saw...

126
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:04,120
is probably real.

127
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:09,230
Police must suspect something's up
with Chairman Park and a politician.

128
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:13,400
That explains the emergency arrest
based on a fake appraisal.

129
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:17,600
Of course, after this,
the deal will likely fall through.

130
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:20,440
It might already have.

131
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:22,670
Chairman Park Tae Ho...

132
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:25,110
must be desperate
to track down the informant...

133
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:26,680
and make them pay.

134
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,710
Who on earth could it be?

135
00:08:30,550 --> 00:08:34,090
Who would have a reason to target
President Kim and Chairman Park...

136
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:36,320
at the same time?

137
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:43,360
Things are about
to get hectic for me.

138
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:47,770
I need you to keep
the business running strong...

139
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:53,100
so the bio division we've secured
doesn't fall apart.

140
00:08:54,310 --> 00:08:58,510
Just in case,
can you look into Secretary Jung?

141
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:02,050
She might have a clue
as to who the informant is.

142
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:04,380
Are you trying to find
the informant yourself?

143
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,820
Before I take advantage
of this situation,

144
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:09,020
I need to confirm a few things.

145
00:09:09,290 --> 00:09:11,290
How do you plan
to use this situation?

146
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:23,270
What should I do with what I found?

147
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:24,600
(Team Leader, Choi Yu Na)

148
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:26,240
I wonder if President Kim knew...

149
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:29,010
about the deal between the chairman
and Assemblyman Kwon.

150
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:32,940
Well, whether she knew or not,

151
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:35,450
she won't tell the police
the chairman was behind it.

152
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,150
It's more likely President Kim...

153
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:41,350
will take the fall
for the fake appraisal.

154
00:09:42,990 --> 00:09:45,990
But what if I call the police
with this evidence?

155
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:50,960
That would put the chairman
in a very tight spot.

156
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:57,740
This could be some serious leverage.

157
00:10:03,070 --> 00:10:04,340
No matter how I look at it,

158
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,750
this incident is definitely
the chairman's weak spot.

159
00:10:08,850 --> 00:10:11,180
Is that
all you've been thinking about?

160
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:14,590
President Kim
is Park Min Jun's mother,

161
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:17,360
and she'll be your mother-in-law
once you're married.

162
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:20,290
Shouldn't you at least pretend
to be concerned?

163
00:10:21,090 --> 00:10:22,990
That's only once we're married.

164
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:27,060
Right now, she's just in the way
of my wedding.

165
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:30,200
You and me both.

166
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:33,100
Are we just thinking about
how to use this?

167
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:38,110
If that's the case,
then I have no choice but to win.

168
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:45,220
I just checked with my dad,
and you're right, Ms. Choi.

169
00:10:46,050 --> 00:10:47,650
Even though the deal fell through,

170
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,790
if their conspiracy comes to light,

171
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:51,190
the fallout will be huge.

172
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:55,530
We should be able to use this
to make Chairman Park budge.

173
00:10:56,490 --> 00:10:59,230
Nice. I knew it.

174
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:03,270
Let's use this opportunity
to put more pressure on him.

175
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:08,040
To clean up this mess,
he'll have to do whatever you say.

176
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,980
That's exactly what I was thinking.

177
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:18,480
Yoon Jung, I packed some food.

178
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:23,950
She won't eat properly in there,
so at least take this.

179
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:26,820
Right.
She'll at least eat your cooking.

180
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:30,030
Toiletries, a blanket,

181
00:11:30,090 --> 00:11:32,630
a change of clothes and...
I've packed all that.

182
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:35,500
And what else should I pack?

183
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:38,170
I've never had to do this before.

184
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,140
This isn't the right time
to be digging for information.

185
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,010
Just pack light.

186
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:46,540
It's hard to get anything
to her anyway.

187
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:48,410
Really?

188
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:50,750
You can't bring in food either.

189
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:54,820
How do you know so much?
Is that from firsthand experience?

190
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:59,220
Why are you calling me a criminal
when I'm only trying to help?

191
00:12:00,020 --> 00:12:02,330
I'm still taking all of it.

192
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:04,200
She probably hasn't eaten anything.

193
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,830
If they won't let me,
I'll make them take it...

194
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,300
and make sure
she gets at least a bite.

195
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:11,770
Take it all and plead with them.

196
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:17,140
Secretary Jung,
if you're ready, let's...

197
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:23,210
I heard about your mother.

198
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:26,750
- She'll be all right.
- Yes, of course.

199
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,290
- We should get going.
- Okay.

200
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,860
Sister, don't forget the food.

201
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,360
Sister?

202
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,800
Oh, that.

203
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,830
He's my younger brother,

204
00:12:40,830 --> 00:12:43,630
but that doesn't matter right now.
Let's go.

205
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,840
Later.

206
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,540
I can't take this.

207
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:52,080
I'm sorry, but please watch
the cafe for me.

208
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:53,480
Yoon Jung, wait for me!

209
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,610
- Why are you giving me this?
- Yoon Jung!

210
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,320
Unbelievable.

211
00:12:59,950 --> 00:13:00,950
My gosh.

212
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:02,890
Still,

213
00:13:03,350 --> 00:13:05,960
at least President Kim has people
who care about her.

214
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,460
If they had met
under better circumstances,

215
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,230
my dear Jin Ju would've been
just as loved.

216
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,310
I heard you were insistent...

217
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:29,710
we meet.

218
00:13:29,810 --> 00:13:30,980
What is this about?

219
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:34,620
I was curious
about the anonymous informant.

220
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:41,130
Forget your curiosity
and focus on your own work.

221
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:45,630
Actually, my curiosity is related
to my work.

222
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:50,730
I suspect one of our competitors
might be targeting President Kim.

223
00:13:52,370 --> 00:13:53,670
A competitor?

224
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:57,910
It's obvious President Kim
was the target.

225
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:04,620
Who else but a competitor stands
to gain the most...

226
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:06,680
by targeting her?

227
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:08,750
But...

228
00:14:09,990 --> 00:14:10,990
But?

229
00:14:11,490 --> 00:14:15,760
How would a competitor have known
it was a fraudulent appraisal?

230
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:17,730
That's the part that doesn't add up.

231
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:21,600
Are you once again implying
it was an inside job?

232
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,900
That doesn't add up either.

233
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:28,670
Your wife wouldn't go so far
as to harm Adele Gallery's business,

234
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:32,510
and there isn't anyone else
looking to take...

235
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:37,510
President Kim down
for their own personal gain.

236
00:14:38,980 --> 00:14:41,820
I came here hoping for answers,

237
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:44,290
but you don't seem
to have any either.

238
00:14:45,190 --> 00:14:47,290
I'll see myself out then.

239
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:06,110
So it's not
about ruining my business,

240
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:08,080
but about targeting Myung Hui...

241
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:11,250
for personal gain?

242
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:14,120
Someone who doesn't care
what happens to Adele...

243
00:15:14,220 --> 00:15:16,750
as long as they get what they want.

244
00:15:19,090 --> 00:15:20,090
Don't tell me...

245
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:34,200
I gave Choi Yu Na
the push she needed...

246
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:37,170
and planted a seed of doubt
in Chairman Park.

247
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:41,750
So, should I go
to the anonymous tipster next?

248
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,960
Look here, Ms. Kim!

249
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:55,060
Who ordered you
to fake the appraisal?

250
00:15:55,230 --> 00:15:56,590
I want the truth.

251
00:15:57,260 --> 00:15:59,130
I've already given my statement.

252
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:02,200
It was entirely my fault.

253
00:16:11,310 --> 00:16:12,310
Yes, sir.

254
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:16,010
What? The chief's orders?

255
00:16:17,950 --> 00:16:19,920
We can't stop now.

256
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:21,890
There's no hard evidence,
but circumstantially...

257
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,420
Understood.

258
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:39,370
It looks like Adele...

259
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:42,810
pulled some strings.

260
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:45,410
I'm sorry.

261
00:16:45,810 --> 00:16:47,510
The investigation may end here,

262
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:50,010
but you should be ashamed
of yourself.

263
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:08,130
(Police)

264
00:17:08,230 --> 00:17:09,700
- Dan Hui!
- Dan Hui.

265
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:10,970
Dan Hui!

266
00:17:14,770 --> 00:17:17,840
I was so worried,
I was losing my mind.

267
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,780
I was worried sick about you.

268
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:22,350
Why did you do this alone again?

269
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,510
I'm sorry.

270
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:25,050
I'm okay.

271
00:17:25,250 --> 00:17:26,280
Unbelievable.

272
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,590
Mother.

273
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,410
Why don't you just come stay
at our place tonight?

274
00:17:58,420 --> 00:18:01,350
If you go home, Chairman Park
will give you an earful.

275
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:02,990
That won't happen.

276
00:18:05,490 --> 00:18:07,120
I won't let it.

277
00:18:10,390 --> 00:18:13,060
Father made you do this, didn't he?

278
00:18:14,430 --> 00:18:16,400
Ultimately, it was my choice.

279
00:18:17,430 --> 00:18:19,900
Is Adele more important than you?

280
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:28,750
It doesn't have to be that way
for you too.

281
00:18:29,650 --> 00:18:32,420
You don't need to get dragged
into this fight.

282
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:42,190
The pain you'll have to endure
is already too great.

283
00:18:43,630 --> 00:18:44,900
When the truth comes out...

284
00:18:45,330 --> 00:18:47,660
that your father killed...

285
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,670
Dr. Baek and Baek Jin Ju,

286
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:55,310
dealing with it alone...

287
00:18:56,210 --> 00:18:57,810
will be hard enough.

288
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:00,910
President Kim.

289
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:11,420
Before you go inside,
could I have a word with you?

290
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:14,890
What is this about?

291
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:18,600
I'd rather speak
to Ms. Kim about it.

292
00:19:27,970 --> 00:19:30,040
Who could've sent the anonymous tip?

293
00:19:31,210 --> 00:19:33,780
Who could orchestrate this,

294
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,050
sending Kim Myung Hui to her doom...

295
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:38,250
and destroying Tae Ho's deal
in one move?

296
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:43,490
There's so much to think about,
my head is going to explode.

297
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:46,360
Jung Ran!

298
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:49,630
President Kim was released
and is on her way.

299
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:51,030
Already?

300
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:54,260
That Park Tae Ho...

301
00:19:54,770 --> 00:19:57,170
He must've gotten antsy
and put pressure on the police.

302
00:19:57,230 --> 00:20:00,140
When she gets back,
don't even go near the main house.

303
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:02,510
You don't want to provoke her...

304
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:05,140
and get framed for tipping off the police
when you didn't.

305
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:07,510
I didn't do anything
to make myself a suspect.

306
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:09,050
Please tell me...

307
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,080
it wasn't you, Mom.

308
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:14,650
Do you really think
I'm that clueless?

309
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:17,920
Your father put so much effort
into this deal.

310
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:20,190
If it failed, I'd go down with him.

311
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:21,590
Why would I be reckless enough
to ruin it?

312
00:20:22,130 --> 00:20:24,130
You'd have to be
a special kind of crazy...

313
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:30,600
What is it?

314
00:20:32,540 --> 00:20:35,770
Could Kim Myung Hui actually
have done something so crazy?

315
00:20:36,170 --> 00:20:39,440
Even now, are you still trying
to mess with her?

316
00:20:39,710 --> 00:20:43,180
She just got back from the police.
Give her a break.

317
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:44,620
Ms. Oh.

318
00:20:45,120 --> 00:20:46,950
Just stay out of this one.

319
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,220
Like you said,

320
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:49,620
if you cross Father on this,

321
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:51,820
a lot of people could get hurt.

322
00:21:10,170 --> 00:21:13,640
The tip came from you, didn't it?

323
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:17,450
That's why you asked me
to handle the bio division.

324
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:22,520
You seem to have the wrong idea.

325
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:27,090
Well, I don't care if you deny it.

326
00:21:27,490 --> 00:21:31,530
I didn't come here to confront you
about why you did it.

327
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,600
I just...

328
00:21:36,430 --> 00:21:37,770
want it to look...

329
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:41,140
like someone else gave the tip.

330
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:47,210
When the chairman asks
about the tipster,

331
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:49,950
just drop one little hint.

332
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:54,520
Say you've only had issues recently
with Oh Jung Ran...

333
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:57,490
and Ms. Choi Yu Na.

334
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:05,260
You still haven't forgiven Ms. Choi?

335
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:07,900
Forgive her?

336
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:13,140
Choi Yu Na hasn't lost a thing,

337
00:22:14,170 --> 00:22:16,670
and she doesn't even show
any remorse or regret.

338
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:19,010
So why...

339
00:22:20,010 --> 00:22:21,580
should I forgive her?

340
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:27,780
This will be
a pretty good deal for you.

341
00:22:28,290 --> 00:22:31,220
Once they pin it on someone else,
you'll be in the clear.

342
00:22:32,090 --> 00:22:33,760
Plus,
you'll have grounds to oppose...

343
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:36,460
Park Min Jun's marriage.

344
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:40,600
On top of that, we'll both...

345
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,930
be holding secrets over each other,

346
00:22:42,930 --> 00:22:44,300
so there's nothing to worry about.

347
00:22:45,470 --> 00:22:47,740
I'll leave it with you then.

348
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:51,880
Chloe, I'm...

349
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:53,910
rejecting your offer.

350
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,750
Why's that?

351
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:04,050
I don't want to drag other people
into my affairs.

352
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:08,790
That goes for Ms. Choi,
and for you too, Chloe.

353
00:23:11,230 --> 00:23:14,060
If you're refusing,
I can't force you.

354
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,530
But in return,

355
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:20,440
please stay out of my way.

356
00:23:23,010 --> 00:23:25,510
Just think of it
as us keeping each other's secrets.

357
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,280
Then...

358
00:23:39,820 --> 00:23:40,820
Chloe.

359
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:48,330
I'm done here, so I'll get going.

360
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:58,240
I wanted to take
the long way around.

361
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:03,610
I wanted to use your mother
to sabotage your wedding,

362
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:09,390
but it looks like
I'll have to step in myself.

363
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:13,590
Even if it means you get hurt again.

364
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,800
I hope you hang in there.

365
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:24,300
What?

366
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:27,640
It's just some comfort
and support...

367
00:24:28,210 --> 00:24:29,410
from one colleague to another.

368
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:48,960
A colleague?

369
00:24:51,390 --> 00:24:52,400
Comfort...

370
00:24:53,530 --> 00:24:54,530
and support?

371
00:25:16,020 --> 00:25:17,420
(Chloe)

372
00:25:23,290 --> 00:25:24,290
It's me.

373
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:26,730
Are you free to meet?

374
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:28,870
Good timing.

375
00:25:29,770 --> 00:25:31,100
I needed to talk to you too.

376
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:50,990
This won't ever happen again.

377
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:53,790
Whoever dared to use...

378
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,690
one of my own people
to ruin my plans...

379
00:25:56,960 --> 00:26:00,730
will be hunted down
and crushed for good.

380
00:26:07,840 --> 00:26:10,170
Myung Hui, who do you think
tipped off the police?

381
00:26:10,770 --> 00:26:12,580
Can you think of anyone...

382
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:15,010
who might hold a grudge against you?

383
00:26:18,250 --> 00:26:19,780
I might...

384
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,420
have someone in mind.

385
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:28,830
Why are you in here again
without my permission?

386
00:26:29,730 --> 00:26:31,960
We can talk about the tipster
together, can't we?

387
00:26:32,530 --> 00:26:35,100
Fine.
Who do you think could've done it?

388
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,800
Kim Myung Hui.

389
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:41,370
Wasn't it you?

390
00:26:48,210 --> 00:26:49,380
That's enough.

391
00:26:50,050 --> 00:26:52,120
Are you really going
to frame someone...

392
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:53,750
who went through all this
because of Father?

393
00:26:58,790 --> 00:27:00,890
Everything happens for a reason.

394
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:04,190
If I staged all this,
wrecked my reputation,

395
00:27:04,860 --> 00:27:06,260
and got myself arrested,

396
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:09,070
wouldn't there have to be
a good reason?

397
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:14,000
If you're going to frame me
as the informant,

398
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:16,610
you should start
by telling me my motive.

399
00:27:17,810 --> 00:27:18,810
Frame you?

400
00:27:19,410 --> 00:27:21,110
As the chairman just said,

401
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:25,650
aren't you the one
with a grudge against me?

402
00:27:26,020 --> 00:27:27,980
I may be crazy,
but I'm not stupid enough...

403
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:29,950
to ruin the gallery's business.

404
00:27:35,130 --> 00:27:37,890
If it's not either of these two...

405
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:43,270
How have things been
between you and Ms. Choi?

406
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:46,600
Sorry?

407
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:49,540
Don't tell me Chloe already...

408
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:52,280
Why bring her up all of a sudden?

409
00:27:53,710 --> 00:27:54,710
Wait.

410
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,310
Come to think of it,
something odd happened.

411
00:27:58,780 --> 00:27:59,880
Something odd?

412
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:02,290
Ms. Choi was at the house.

413
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:04,120
She walked out of your study...

414
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:05,860
right after Kim Myung Hui
got arrested.

415
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:28,080
(World Gemological Institute)

416
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:38,050
Someone definitely touched it.

417
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:41,620
She knows
about the fake appraisal report,

418
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:43,260
the exclusive development rights,

419
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:46,060
and even the lobbying documents?

420
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:50,530
She came to the house
the day of the arrest, of all days,

421
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:53,300
and got hold of these?

422
00:28:55,940 --> 00:28:56,940
(Hamlet)

423
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:07,880
Get Ms. Choi in here right now!

424
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:15,260
(Hamlet)

425
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:21,360
Why did you want to meet here?

426
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,570
I figured you'd be nearby.

427
00:29:24,670 --> 00:29:25,670
Could it be...

428
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:29,040
My family's all gathered inside.

429
00:29:31,210 --> 00:29:33,180
Since it's rare for all of them
to be together,

430
00:29:34,580 --> 00:29:35,780
I was hoping to tell them today.

431
00:29:38,410 --> 00:29:39,420
That's funny.

432
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:42,650
I called to say
the exact same thing.

433
00:29:43,020 --> 00:29:44,550
Is that really why you called?

434
00:29:47,390 --> 00:29:51,030
To create a rift
between Choi Yu Na and Park Tae Ho,

435
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:55,570
and to stop her and Park Min Jun
from getting married...

436
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,270
Let's go in.

437
00:30:03,570 --> 00:30:05,740
All right, here goes.

438
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:07,610
I'm joining the Adele family.

439
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:24,390
Ms. Choi came by
after I was arrested.

440
00:30:24,730 --> 00:30:26,130
How could she report it...

441
00:30:26,130 --> 00:30:27,560
if the appraisal report's
still here?

442
00:30:28,670 --> 00:30:31,530
She could've called in a tip
using a forged appraisal report...

443
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:34,900
and then tried to steal the original
as more definitive proof.

444
00:30:35,840 --> 00:30:38,510
Her snooping around the study
is already a huge issue.

445
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:43,010
First that incident with Chloe,
and now this.

446
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:45,520
Choi Yu Na is not someone
we can trust at all.

447
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:48,480
If she's done something wrong,
she must be punished accordingly.

448
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:51,550
And please put an end
to my engagement.

449
00:30:56,890 --> 00:31:00,000
I was going to let her slide
until I got the recorder back,

450
00:31:00,260 --> 00:31:03,070
but that audacious girl
is growing increasingly bold.

451
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:06,200
I'll take this chance
to crush her for good...

452
00:31:06,870 --> 00:31:08,810
and get the recorder back.

453
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,630
Hyun Jun, you...

454
00:31:36,570 --> 00:31:38,000
Since everyone's here,

455
00:31:38,970 --> 00:31:40,240
I have some good news to share.

456
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,480
Chloe and I...

457
00:31:49,450 --> 00:31:50,450
are getting married.

458
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:54,350
Park Hyun Jun!

459
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,120
What in the world?

460
00:32:42,600 --> 00:32:45,670
(Pearl in Red)

461
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:49,040
You'll marry her?
I said no to marrying that vixen.

462
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:50,110
Mom!

463
00:32:50,210 --> 00:32:52,110
- What game are you playing?
- The anonymous tip!

464
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:55,910
He's under the impression
that Ms. Choi tipped off the police.

465
00:32:56,150 --> 00:32:57,780
Did you set her up in advance?

466
00:32:57,810 --> 00:33:01,350
Ms. Choi and Chloe both want
to marry into the family,

467
00:33:01,650 --> 00:33:04,990
but I'll only accept
whoever proves more capable.

468
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:06,820
- Chloe!
- Either compete...

469
00:33:06,820 --> 00:33:08,220
or give up on marrying my son.

470
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:11,260
Anyone who objects can leave
my house right now!

471
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:14,800
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
